### HEALTH
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────
### USUARIOS
### ─────────────────────────────────────

### 1) Registrar usuario
POST http://localhost:3000/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "pablo@bildy.com",
  "password": "Pass1234!"
}

###

### 2) Validar email (usa el verificationCode del registro)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/user/validation
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "code": "123456"
}

###

### 3) Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "pablo@bildy.com",
  "password": "Pass1234!"
}

###

### 4) Obtener perfil propio
GET http://localhost:3000/api/user/me
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 5) Actualizar datos personales
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/user/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "name": "Pablo",
  "lastName": "Franco",
  "nif": "12345678A"
}

###

### 6) Crear o actualizar empresa
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/user/company
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "name": "Bildy Obras SL",
  "cif": "B12345678",
  "address": {
    "street": "Calle Mayor",
    "number": "12",
    "postal": "28001",
    "city": "Madrid",
    "province": "Madrid"
  },
  "isFreelance": false
}

###

### 7) Subir logo empresa (usar Postman/Thunder Client con form-data)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/user/logo
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 8) Cambiar contraseña
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/user/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "oldPassword": "Pass1234!",
  "newPassword": "NuevoPass1!"
}

###

### 9) Refresh token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/user/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "REFRESH_TOKEN"
}

###

### 10) Logout
POST http://localhost:3000/api/user/logout
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 11) Soft delete usuario
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/user?soft=true
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 12) Hard delete usuario
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/user
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────
### CLIENTES
### ─────────────────────────────────────

### 13) Crear cliente
POST http://localhost:3000/api/client
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "name": "Constructora ABC",
  "cif": "A12345678",
  "email": "contacto@abc.com",
  "phone": "612345678",
  "address": {
    "street": "Calle Gran Vía",
    "number": "45",
    "postal": "28013",
    "city": "Madrid",
    "province": "Madrid"
  }
}

###

### 14) Listar clientes (con paginación y filtros)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/client?page=1&limit=10&sort=-createdAt
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 15) Listar clientes filtrados por nombre
GET http://localhost:3000/api/client?name=Constructora
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 16) Obtener cliente por id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/client/CLIENT_ID
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 17) Actualizar cliente
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/client/CLIENT_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "name": "Constructora ABC Actualizada",
  "phone": "699999999"
}

###

### 18) Soft delete cliente
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/client/CLIENT_ID?soft=true
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 19) Hard delete cliente
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/client/CLIENT_ID
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 20) Listar clientes archivados
GET http://localhost:3000/api/client/archived
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 21) Restaurar cliente archivado
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/client/CLIENT_ID/restore
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────
### PROYECTOS
### ─────────────────────────────────────

### 22) Crear proyecto
POST http://localhost:3000/api/project
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "name": "Reforma Oficinas Centro",
  "projectCode": "PRJ-001",
  "client": "CLIENT_ID",
  "email": "obra@abc.com",
  "notes": "Reforma completa de la planta baja",
  "address": {
    "street": "Calle Alcalá",
    "number": "100",
    "postal": "28009",
    "city": "Madrid",
    "province": "Madrid"
  }
}

###

### 23) Listar proyectos (con paginación y filtros)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/project?page=1&limit=10&sort=-createdAt
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 24) Filtrar proyectos por cliente y estado
GET http://localhost:3000/api/project?client=CLIENT_ID&active=true
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 25) Obtener proyecto por id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/project/PROJECT_ID
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 26) Actualizar proyecto
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/project/PROJECT_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "name": "Reforma Oficinas Centro - Fase 2",
  "notes": "Incluye planta primera"
}

###

### 27) Soft delete proyecto
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/project/PROJECT_ID?soft=true
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 28) Hard delete proyecto
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/project/PROJECT_ID
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 29) Listar proyectos archivados
GET http://localhost:3000/api/project/archived
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 30) Restaurar proyecto archivado
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/project/PROJECT_ID/restore
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────
### ALBARANES
### ─────────────────────────────────────

### 31) Crear albarán de materiales
POST http://localhost:3000/api/deliverynote
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "format": "material",
  "description": "Entrega de materiales para cimentación",
  "material": "Cemento Portland",
  "quantity": 50,
  "unit": "sacos",
  "workDate": "2026-05-06",
  "client": "CLIENT_ID",
  "project": "PROJECT_ID"
}

###

### 32) Crear albarán de horas
POST http://localhost:3000/api/deliverynote
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "format": "hours",
  "description": "Jornada de albañilería",
  "hours": 8,
  "workers": [
    { "name": "Juan García", "hours": 8 },
    { "name": "Pedro López", "hours": 6 }
  ],
  "workDate": "2026-05-06",
  "client": "CLIENT_ID",
  "project": "PROJECT_ID"
}

###

### 33) Listar albaranes (con paginación y filtros)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/deliverynote?page=1&limit=10&sort=-workDate
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 34) Filtrar albaranes por proyecto, formato y firmado
GET http://localhost:3000/api/deliverynote?project=PROJECT_ID&format=hours&signed=false
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 35) Filtrar albaranes por rango de fechas
GET http://localhost:3000/api/deliverynote?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 36) Obtener albarán por id (con populate)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/deliverynote/NOTE_ID
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 37) Descargar PDF de albarán
GET http://localhost:3000/api/deliverynote/pdf/NOTE_ID
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 38) Firmar albarán (usar Postman/Thunder Client con form-data)
### Campo: signature (tipo File, imagen PNG/JPG)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/deliverynote/NOTE_ID/sign
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### 39) Eliminar albarán (solo si no está firmado)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/deliverynote/NOTE_ID
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

###

